<del rend="strikethrough"> cʒu <expan>dyſe<ex>n</ex>hofen</expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_206_r1l34">
<del rend="strikethrough">aufgehal </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_206_r1l33">die man Jn bey Schafhauſen </ab></add>
                        aufgehalten vnd genomen het / <del rend="strikethrough"><expan>dieſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Senſen </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_206_r1l32">vnd die </ab></add> Jr / den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_206_r1l35">
<expan>ſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ~ die das getan <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        / <del rend="strikethrough">ge </del> wıder <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        / vnd dıe gen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_206_r1l36">Dẏſenhofen braht habt / <del rend="strikethrough">laſſen wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> wiſſen / daʒ </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_206_r1l37">
<add>Nu</add>
<add><ab facs="#facs_206_line_1575971123317_446">hat </ab></add> der
