</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_206_r1l38">behabt <del rend="strikethrough">hat </del> / das die
                        ſein vnd <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> ſein Alſo daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_206_r1l39">khein auſʒman <expan>wed<ex>er</ex></expan> teil noch
                        gemein daran hab / <expan>Dar<ex>ümb</ex></expan>
<expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ </ab>
