</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_206" id="101v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Herman Truchsessen von Dysenhofen </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber her Truchsesz, uns hat fürgelegt Herdegen
                            <expan>Valczn<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, wie <add>er <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>Hanse<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Starke<ex>n</ex></expan> und <expan>sein<ex>er</ex></expan>
                            gesellschaft</add> czwey vasz mit sensen, in dem
                            <expan>eine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>sechshund<ex>er</ex>t</expan> und in <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> v<hi rend="sup">c</hi> und xxxv sensein sein,
                            <add>bevolhen hab</add>, <add>die man in bey Schafhausen</add>
                        aufgehalten und genomen het <add>und die</add> ir den
                            <expan>selb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, die das getan
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, wider <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                        die gen Dysenhofen braht habt. <add>Nu</add>
<add>hat</add> der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sensen vor
                        uns czu den <expan>heilig<ex>en</ex></expan> behabt, das die sein und
                                <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> sein, also daz khein auszman
                                <expan>wed<ex>er</ex></expan> teil noch gemein daran hab.
                                <expan>Dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir dem
                            <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein
                        sensen <expan>widergeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und <expan>volge<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        lassen wollet <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>. Auch <pb facs="#facs_207" id="102r"/> so
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns etlich die
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wol gesagt und czuwissen getan, wie ir ew
                                    <add><expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan></add> in den und auch
                        vormals in <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> der <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>sach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gar gunstiklichen <add>und
                                    <expan>fr<ex>euntlichen</ex></expan></add> beweiset habt, des
                        wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleisz
                                <expan>danke<ex>n</ex></expan> und begern, das ümb
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>allcz<ex>eit</ex></expan> czu verdienen.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in die
                            <expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan>
<expan>Georii</expan>
<expan>a<ex>nno</ex></expan> ix<hi rend="sup">no</hi>.</ab>
</div>
